  PROPPATCH Method - Motivation  
      A mechanism is needed to create properties
 
  As PUT isnï¿½t really suitable for creating properties, a mechanism is still needed to create properties.
       Atomicity
 
  Most property scenarios require a way to atomically create and delete a number of properties in order to keep the resource in a consistent state.       
 
